comments.content: This pathway shows the molecular details on the human Fact complex and DNA double-strand break (repair). These processes are involved in the Tessadori-Bicknell-van Haaften syndrome 3 (TEBINVAD) - for an overview of this syndrome see [WP5575](http://wikipathways.org/instance/WP5575).
